32:55.975 --> 33:03.413
(machine beeping steadily)

33:03.415 --> 33:06.483
(alex) bowl.
Here you go.

33:06.485 --> 33:09.586
Okay. So the cyst
has marsupialized,

33:09.588 --> 33:13.223
And this mess is cleaned up.

33:13.225 --> 33:15.158
Just need to grab
the vessel loops.

33:15.160 --> 33:17.594
At least maggie
didn't pull them out, too.

33:17.596 --> 33:22.232
