I'm on the right path.

36:48.473 --> 36:50.707
Thank you, doctor.

36:50.709 --> 36:52.242
You saved me.

36:56.681 --> 37:01.952
It's okay. I'm a nun.

37:01.954 --> 37:04.588
I screwed everything up.

37:04.590 --> 37:05.922
You didn't.

37:05.924 --> 37:07.591
