about my feelings, gavin.

37:26.645 --> 37:28.545
Then talk
about something else.

37:28.547 --> 37:32.649
Anything.

37:32.651 --> 37:35.452
My stepmother
wore a miniskirt.

37:35.454 --> 37:37.520
To the funeral?
Yeah.

37:37.522 --> 37:38.922
It was up to here.

37:38.924 --> 37:42.459
