39:23.095 --> 39:26.429
Gone. So gone.

39:26.431 --> 39:27.430
Could I get a hug?

39:27.432 --> 39:29.366
Okay.

39:29.368 --> 39:31.034
There we go.

39:31.036 --> 39:32.736
